channel.title: RSCEvolution - Evolution awaits you. -Closed Due to Issues with Paypal back soon
channel.description:
[center][b]Intro[/b][/center] [center]RSCEvolution is a server made for the purpose of having a fun time. Its based off of Noobscape Final due to all of its features and easy administration. This is a brand new server striving to gain players, please invite your friends.[/center]
[center][b]Ranks and how they work[/b][/center] [center]To become part of the staff team you must show loyalty, respect towards other members, be well liked, and have a good attitude towards things. there is no way to purchase staff nor will there ever be only those who show what we are looking for will be offered a staff position.
Below are a list of ranks and how to earn them [/center]
[ul][li]Event Staff - Event staff are certain individuals who help maintain and run events, They are generally active at most events and are friendly so dont hesitate to ask them questions!. If you are part of the event staff you are generally looked upon first if the administrators are looking for a new Player Moderator[/li]
[li]Player Mod - Player Moderators are the lowest rank of moderators who have abilities almost the same as runescape's, they do have the ability to use the mute command but are informed that they should tell someone higher than them unless its completely necessary[/li]
[li]Moderators- Moderators are players who help moderate the server from rule breakers, the have far more commands and moderation abilities than player moderators and do not need to report to higher authority when using the ::ban or ::mute command.[/li]
[li]Administrators - Are the highest ranked players in the game, they have access to all the commands and are general veteran players who have worked there ranks up from moderator[/li]
[li]Developer - Developers help add new and unique content to the server, they have no moderation abilities and are not very high up in the food chain, but we do respect our developers as without them we would be no were.[/li]
[li]Subscribers - These re people who have sent in 5.00 to help maintain and run the server, they get 50% more xp, there fatigue drains slower, Access to a subscriber only area with more npcs that drop rare items[/li][/ul]
To Become Part of the staff team you must have served as the position under you for at least 1 week (Excluding Player Moderator and Event staff) and must be accepted by the majority of the current staff.
[center][b]Additional Information[/b][/center]
[ul][li]XP Rate - 300x[/li] [li]Drops - fare and will be edited over time[/li] [li]Forums at http://72.189.211.97[/li] [li]24/7[/li][/ul]
[center][b]Wilderness Information[/b][/center]
[ul][li]The Wilderness is F2P on Monday, Tuesday, Thursday, and Saturday[/li] [li]The Wilderness is P2P on Wednesday, Friday, and Sunday[/li][/ul]
[center][b]Rules[/b][/center]
[ul][li]Rule 1. - Racism/Sexist comments will not be tolerated and will result in a PERMANENT Mute.[/li]
[li]Rule 2. - Profanity of any kind will be tolerated, but not if said profanity is directed towards other members. This will result in a mute ranging from 3-5 days depending on the severity of the offense[/li]
[li]Rule 3. - Spamming the chat box or ::say command is not allowed and will result in a 24 hour mute[/li]
[li]Rule 3. - Advertising of any kind is not allowed and is taken very seriously, if you are caught advertising you will be IPBanned forever[/li]
[li]Rule 4. - Using any kind of Third Party software to access the game such as macro's or cheat clients will result in the user being Permanently IPBanned[/li]
[li]Rule 5. - Decompiling or Altering any of the files provided with the client is not allowed and will result in a 5-10 day mute[/li]
[li]Rule 6. - Do not ask members of the staff team to "Warp" or "Spawn" you items as they are not allowed to do so under ANY circumstance[/li]
[li]Rule 7. - Bug Abuse is not going to be tolerated, if you find a bug post it on the forums[/li]
[li]Rule 8. - Trading RSCEvolution items for anything not related to RSCEvolution is prohibited[/li]
[li]Rule 9. - The act of sharing your account or items is at your own risk, we have no obligation to return items if you loose them due to item lending/Account sharing/[/li]
[li]Rule 10. - Item Scamming or Duplication is prohibited and will result in a 20 day ban and a full account wipe[/li][/ul]
[center][b]Pictures[/b][/center] [img]http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/155/rscepicture1.jpg/[/img] Sorry about the lack of pictures im busy and cant bother right now, ill post more soon. or if any one would be kind enough to do it for me.
[center][b]Latest Download Link[/b][/center] http://72.189.211.97/download
NOTE: Forums are currently under maintenance and will have no board topics ect, feel free to register as i will be working on them today. server is still up. The level cap may be raised depending on what the majority of the players want. Rares will be introduced into the economy once there are atleast 25 people online ill proceed to drop 3 party hats 1 mask and a santa to start that and then hold events from then to release more ect.
